= seven

Course homework submission website.


== Installation

Follow the standard steps for setting up a Rails development environment.
    git clone
    bundle install
    rake db:create db:migrate

The command below runs the development server. Ctrl+C stops it.
    rails s

The first user registered on the system automatically receives administrative
privileges. Course specifics can be configured by selecting Setup > Course in
the left-side menu.


== Development

Much of the CSS running this site is at https://github.com/pwnstyles. If you
want to change it, clone the repository in a sibling directory to seven, and
bundler will find the clone and use it. Refreshing the page will reflect any
CSS changes that you make.
